text: Bulyak () is a rural locality (a village) in Saraysinsky Selsoviet, Sterlibashevsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 33 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 33 km from Sterlibashevo, 5 km from Yelimbetovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Sterlibashevsky District
title: Bulyak, Sterlibashevsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
